name: Laundry Day
description: A penny saved is a penny earned. A laundered $100 dollar United States bill printed on a towel hangs to dry. So much revolves around money, printed numbers on paper, that it runs our world. My camera captures this faded wet version hanging in the sun that leads me to wonder what its all about here in this place and time with a photograph to share with you here and now. 4000x4000 pixels 300 dpi Digital Jpeg Photograph and story by Zoran Milich.
